{"tid":1966191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年理大圍城的士司機接載FA時受傷","createTime":"2020-04-10T04:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T18:51:30.000Z","uid":352010,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51cd1872e2a863e1b0b25aff7aef53d4f1d8a94a","tid":1966191,"uid":352010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"本人於<strong>2019年11月18日約上午5:20在紅磡機利士南路與曲街交界處</strong>，駕駛的士接載一名年約25歲男性FA前往將軍澳時，因有需要而要下車時<strong>被相信來自催淚鎗的强大氣流沖至整個人仆低，左肩脫較</strong>。由於公司要求，本人便在上述乘客的急救及照顧下用慢速駛回將軍澳交更地。本人其後入急症室治療，至今尚未康復，左手仍未能完全活動。本人現考慮對有關當局索償，急請以上乘客電郵lcnpeterng@yahoo.com.hk與本人聯絡。謝謝。"},{"pid":"a8d5fafe27da7bf8d83259a4b4e3840a640cbc96","tid":1966191,"uid":73058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f4fe0f63f2aa835eea1402f21682359a622faf","tid":1966191,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"baae25a20796274c39dd1db2127948467e105733","tid":1966191,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c1a70cddc105f5762e7d1e7fbc3e59f737fa45","tid":1966191,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/